mina","e":"of"},{"b":"11.","c":"الْءَاخِرَةِ","d":"l-ākhirati","e":"the Hereafter"},{"b":"15.7","c":"كَمَا","d":"kamā","e":"as"},{"b":"16.3","c":"يَئِسَ","d":"ya-isa","e":"despair"},{"b":"17.2","c":"الْكُفَّارُ","d":"l-kufāru","e":"the disbelievers"},{"b":"18.4","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"of"},{"b":"18.8","c":"أَصْحَابِ","d":"aṣḥābi","e":"(the) companions"},{"b":"19.9","c":"الْقُبُورِ","d":"l-qubūri","e":"(of) the graves"}],"a":{"g":"O you who have believed, do not make allies of a people with whom Allah has become angry. They have despaired of [reward in] the Hereafter just as the disbelievers have despaired of [meeting] the inhabitants of the graves."}}}